  "metadata": {
    "name": "Verify No netrc Files Exist",
    "description": "The <tt>.netrc</tt> files contain login information\nused to auto-login into FTP servers and reside in the user's home\ndirectory. These files may contain unencrypted passwords to\nremote FTP servers making them susceptible to access by unauthorized\nusers and should not be used.  Any <tt>.netrc</tt> files should be removed.",
    "rationale": "Unencrypted passwords for remote FTP servers may be stored in <tt>.netrc</tt>\nfiles.",
